    "ArticleTitle": "Effect of a short-term psychological intervention on the anxiety and depression of amyotrophic lateral sclerosis patients.",
    "Pagination": {
      "StartPage": "1426",
      "EndPage": "1435",
      "MedlinePgn": "1426-35"
